{"@context": "http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld", "id": "urn:uuid:1c83aa83-6bad-4d79-9140-524683ebc562", "type": "Annotation", "created": "2026-03-13T00:53:53.123404+00:00", "creator": {"type": "Person", "name": "human"}, "target": {"selector": {"type": "TextQuoteSelector", "exact": "Inline math (escaped parens):\n()", "prefix": ")logQ(x)P(x)\u200b\nLaTeX\\LaTeXLATE\u200bX\n", "suffix": "\nDisplay math (double dollar sig"}}, "body": [{"type": "TextualBody", "value": "\\(...\\) and \\[...\\] aren't default math delimiters\n  in pandoc.\n\n  Pandoc's markdown only recognizes $...$ and $$...$$ by\n   default. To enable the TeX-style \\(...\\) / \\[...\\]\n  delimiters, you need the tex_math_single_backslash\n  extension:\n\n  pandoc --katex --standalone\n  --from=markdown+tex_math_single_backslash --to=html\n  test.md -o test.html", "creator": {"type": "Person", "name": "human"}, "created": "2026-03-13T00:53:53.123404+00:00"}], "scholia:status": "open"}
{"@context": "http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld", "id": "urn:uuid:1c83aa83-6bad-4d79-9140-524683ebc562", "type": "Annotation", "created": "2026-03-13T00:53:53.123404+00:00", "creator": {"type": "Person", "name": "human"}, "target": {"selector": {"type": "TextQuoteSelector", "exact": "Inline math (escaped parens):\n()", "prefix": ")logQ(x)P(x)\u200b\nLaTeX\\LaTeXLATE\u200bX\n", "suffix": "\nDisplay math (double dollar sig"}}, "body": [{"type": "TextualBody", "value": "\\(...\\) and \\[...\\] aren't default math delimiters\n  in pandoc.\n\n  Pandoc's markdown only recognizes $...$ and $$...$$ by\n   default. To enable the TeX-style \\(...\\) / \\[...\\]\n  delimiters, you need the tex_math_single_backslash\n  extension:\n\n  pandoc --katex --standalone\n  --from=markdown+tex_math_single_backslash --to=html\n  test.md -o test.html", "creator": {"type": "Person", "name": "human"}, "created": "2026-03-13T00:53:53.123404+00:00"}, {"type": "TextualBody", "value": "Fixed \u2014 added +tex_math_single_backslash to the Pandoc --from flag. Restart the server and both $...$ and \\(...\\) / \\[...\\] delimiters should work now.", "creator": {"type": "Software", "name": "ai"}, "created": "2026-03-13T00:54:24.786127+00:00"}], "scholia:status": "open", "modified": "2026-03-13T00:54:24.786127+00:00"}
